complexityAnalysis.taskTitle: Investigate and Fix Application Errors on Vercel and Localhost
complexityAnalysis.expansionPrompt: Break down the debugging process into distinct subtasks: 1. Reproduce errors on Vercel, 2. Reproduce errors on localhost, 3. Perform client-side debugging, 4. Conduct server-side debugging, 5. Review configurations, 6. Document findings.
complexityAnalysis.reasoning: This task involves multiple layers of debugging across different environments, requiring a systematic approach to identify and resolve issues. Each step can be complex and may require separate focus.
